sentences.english: Any of about 100 species of small, slender freshwater fishes (family Percidae), native to eastern North America.

sentences.english: Meanwhile, Congress had also become involved in the fate of the snail darter.

sentences.english: I can use it like a boomerang to keep him in line.

sentences.english: Jango had used an exotic weapon, a Kamino saberdart, to eliminate Zam.

sentences.english: As she ran to pick, once harpooned , the fishermen nicknamed the poor whale.
